---
title: Rustic Sausage Gnocchi with Baked Parmesan Crisps
description: Gnocchi are little pillowy potato dumplings that are delicious when doused with sauce. We're jazzing up this recipe by taking gnocchi a step further – pan-frying them until they're crispy and golden-brown. The crispy gnocchi and sausage bring a whole new meaning to the word: 'delicious.' Topped with home-baked Parmesan crisps, you won't believe this meal was homemade!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gnocchis-rustiques-a-la-saucisse-bb58708d.jpg
